data.description: Move right in to this charming 2 bedroom 2 bath home in the beautiful 55+ gated community of Leisure Knoll. Renovated in 2022. This home has an open concept kitchen and LR. Kitchen has quartz countertops including peninsula and  stainless steel appliances, included. Off the kitchen is a four season room. Plantation shutters throughout this home. Cohesive laminate  flooring. Keypad outside garage.  Solar panels. Security lights. New irrigation system. Leisure Knoll offers a vibrant lifestyle & many amenities to enjoy.
